<h2 id="section-top">Geriatric Medicine</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1431">Lewisham and Greenwich NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Elderly Care Outpatients<br/>020 8333 3379</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent0785b48acff24cceb2b96b7a04cefc3b">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Elderly Care" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1933"/>
</div>
</div>
<p class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><strong>Outpatient services for the elderly are situated within the main hospital’s outpatient area and the new Kingfisher building. We have a number of specialist services as outlined below. </strong></p>
<p class="ImmTextAlign_Left">We also run general medicine for the elderly clinics where we are happy to see patients over the age of 65 with medical problems.</p>
<p class="ImmTextAlign_Left"> </p>
<p><strong>What services are available?</strong></p>
<p>The Trust provide a comprehensive outpatient service, including:</p>
<ul>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#FallsClinic">Falls Clinic</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#MovementDisorders">Movement Disorders Clinic</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#Neurovascular">TIA Clinic</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#MemoryClinic">Memory Clinic</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#ElderlyMedicine">Elderly Clinic</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#StrokeUnit">Stroke Unit</a> </li>
<li class="ImmTextAlign_Left"><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx#FracturedNeck">Fractured Neck or Femur Service</a> </li>
</ul>
<p class="ImmTextAlign_Left"> </p>
<p><strong>Further information</strong></p>
<p>For further information, including clinic times, referral details and key staff, please <strong><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/acute__elderly_medicine/elderly_care_outpatients.aspx">visit the elderly care of our website</a></strong>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
